Obama Is ‘Anti-Business,’ 3M’s CEO Buckley Says, FT Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-02-28T02:43:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/obama-is-anti-business-3m-s-ceo-buckley-says-ft-reports.html
  3M Co . Chief Executive Officer  George Buckley  said President  Barack Obama  is “anti-business”
and manufacturers may leave to set up operations in Mexico or  Canada  if the U.S. business environment is “hostile,” the
Financial Times reported, citing an interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
